title: NFL Week 5 picks against the spread, DFS advice (Football 10/05)
description:
Will Brinson breaks down the Patriots and Colts game before welcoming on Nick Kostos for the Fastest 18 Minutes as the guys break down their six best bets of the week from the NFL, fantasy, DFS, sides, totals, whatever. Then Pete Prisco and R.J. White join Will to pick every single game against the spread for the SuperContest.
